ks after a siege of ten years; according to classical legend, a few Trojan survivors got away to found Rome (and, according to medieval legend, another group founded Britain)."]}]},{"name":"de","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Bright’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Drue de Montacute was born in 1253, in Boveney, Buckinghamshire, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son with ?."},"et":{"<1253>–":"1253–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1279–Male":"1279–Surnud","1253–Male":"1253–Surnud","<1279>":"1279","1279":"1279","1253":"1253","<1253>":"1253","<of Boveney, Bucks, ENG>":"Boveney, Buckinghamshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"<1253>–":"1253–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1279–Male":"1279–Kuollut","1253–Male":"1253–Kuollut","<1279>":"1279","1279":"1279","1253":"1253","<1253>":"1253","<of Boveney, Bucks, ENG>":"Boveney, Buckinghamshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"<1253>–":"1253–Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1279–Male":"1279–Décédé","1253–Male":"1253–Décédé","<1279>":"1279","1279":"1279","1253":"1253","<1253>":"1253","<of Boveney, Bucks, ENG>":"Boveney, Buckinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Drue de Montacute est né en 1253, à Boveney, Buckinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec ?."},"de":{"<1253>–":"1253–Verstorben","–Female":"Verstorben","1279–Male":"1279–Verstorben","1253–Male":"1253–Verstorben","<1279>":"1279","1279":"1279","1253":"1253","<1253>":"1253","<of Boveney, Bucks, ENG>":"Boveney, Buckinghamshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Drue de Montacute wurde 1253 in Boveney, Buckinghamshire, England, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mit ? mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"<1253>–":"1253–Desede","–Female":"Desede","1279–Male":"1279–Desede","1253–Male":"1253–Desede","<1279>":"1279","1279":"1279","1253":"1253","<1253>":"1253","<of Boveney, Bucks, ENG>":"Boveney, Buckinghamshire, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu"